        {
            "id": 5900918,
            "title": "《拋空追蹤》半日拋空213億元佔大市成交13%,騰訊佔8%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社14日專訊》港股半日成交1589.58億元,股票拋空213.04億元,佔大市成交13.4%,拋空股份有683隻。騰訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00700:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00700\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00700-HK</a>)及阿里(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09988:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09988\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09988-HK</a>)拋空較多,各有17.12億元及13.51億元,各佔總額約8.04%及6.34%,佔各自股份成交的18.5%及16.63%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　南方恒生科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03033:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03033\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03033-HK</a>)及盈富基金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02800:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02800\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02800-HK</a>)各有拋空13.47億元及10.46億元,各佔總額約6.32%及4.91%,佔各自股份成交的49.58%及24.06%。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　騰訊收報527元,升19.5元,或3.84%;阿里收報136.3元,升4.8元,或3.65%;南方恒生科技收報5.78元,升0.165元,或2.94%;盈富基金收報24.38元,升0.62元,或2.61%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
